casebody.data:
Tuesday, May 14, 1996

MOTION DOCKET

96-959. Benner v. Hammond.

Ross County, No. 96CA2116. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution of the court of appeals’ judgment,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, denied.

Resnick and Stratton, JJ., dissent.
